value: Southern California, coastal Texas, southern Louisiana, and southern Florida, south along both coasts of Mexico to Oaxaca and Campeche; Honduras; Cuba. South America from Colombia south to Peru and east to the Guianas; Para, Brazil, south to northern and central Argentina, Paraguay, and Uruguay; Trinidad. Eastern Africa from Sudan to Natal; Madagascar. India and Sri Lanka (Ceylon); Burma south to Pegu. Recent wintering movements in central and eastern United States.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Resident, marshes and swamps: Senegal - Sudan in Sahel zone and south to E South Africa in eastern half of continent.
Shallow waters (both fresh and brackish), preferring marshes, lagoons, and wet and flooded cultivated fields (primarily Tropical Zone.)
marshes, flooded grassland, grassy lagoons, forest
